name: Chefchaouen, Morocco
description:
Welcome to a holiday in the warm Chefchaouen in Morocco. Come and join a relaxing role-playing tourist experience! Check out famous photo spots, grab a cool drink, or perhaps take a dive in the pool and unwind in the afternoon sun. 

The map was made for the City Building Jam
